eam/apps/1917550/extras/9a81b5d1b65216f9c484ffea28ea4461.mp4?t=1756929569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Attention to environmental details<br></li><li>The world of art that you can enter<br></li><li>Environmental interactivity<br></li><li>Random events during the passage<br></li><li>Partial non-linearity of the game</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1917550/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1756929569\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1917550/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1756929569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1917550/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1756929569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
